Come back and keep fighting!

812
00:36:15,080 --> 00:36:15,696
What are you saying!

813
00:36:15,720 --> 00:36:16,896
Are you still human?

814
00:36:16,920 --> 00:36:18,496
Seeing your fellow citizen being bullied...

815
00:36:18,520 --> 00:36:19,376
not coming out to lend a hand...

816
00:36:19,400 --> 00:36:20,656
instead, you are on the side making sarcastic remarks.

817
00:36:20,680 --> 00:36:22,016
Are you still Chinese?

818
00:36:22,040 --> 00:36:24,400
Do still know what shame is?

819
00:36:27,000 --> 00:36:28,336
You know what shame is,

820
00:36:28,360 --> 00:36:30,176
what's the point of showing off here?

821
00:36:30,200 --> 00:36:32,336
If you have the ability fight a battle in Europe,

822
00:36:32,360 --> 00:36:34,096
you would exterminate the Eight-Nation Alliance.

823
00:36:34,120 --> 00:36:34,496
That's right!

824
00:36:34,520 --> 00:36:35,456
That's what is called ability.

825
00:36:35,480 --> 00:36:36,256
You!

826
00:36:36,280 --> 00:36:37,376
What do you want to do?

827
00:36:37,400 --> 00:36:39,216
A Chinese people fighting each other

828
00:36:39,240 --> 00:36:40,016
Come

829
00:36:40,040 --> 00:36:42,016
Let foreigners properly see...

830
00:36:42,040 --> 00:36:44,096
how Chinese people bully each other

831
00:36:44,120 --> 00:36:45,840
Come

832
00:36:47,000 --> 00:36:48,016
Do you see it?

833
00:36:48,040 --> 00:36:49,616
Chinese people are bullying each other!

834
00:36:49,640 --> 00:36:50,816
Come  Everyone come see

835
00:36:50,840 --> 00:36:52,800
Stop quarrelling, all of you go back for me

836
00:36:52,840 --> 00:36:54,016
Let's go

837
00:36:54,040 --> 00:36:54,790
All of you go back

838
00:36:54,814 --> 00:36:56,177
All of you go back

839
00:36:56,440 --> 00:36:59,200
Don't be angry, don't lower yourself to their level

840
00:37:02,760 --> 00:37:04,560
Make way

841
00:37:04,920 --> 00:37:06,896
Raise your feet a little

842
00:37:06,920 --> 00:37:08,720
You stepped on my tile

843
00:37:12,120 --> 00:37:14,000
What tile?

844
00:37:14,360 --> 00:37:17,840
Little... Little chick it seems like

845
00:37:23,880 --> 00:37:26,400
This eyesight of yours is not good

846
00:37:27,480 --> 00:37:29,520
It's a cake

847
00:37:29,720 --> 00:37:31,360
Play often?

848
00:37:32,520 --> 00:37:34,480
Why did you throw the tile!

849
00:37:34,600 --> 00:37:36,560
Fellow citizens being insulted

850
00:37:36,600 --> 00:37:38,256
is far less important

851
00:37:38,280 --> 00:37:40,736
than your mahjong game, is it?

852
00:37:40,760 --> 00:37:42,416
What does this hell does have to do with playing Mahjong!

853
00:37:42,440 --> 00:37:43,376
What did you throw my tile for?

854
00:37:43,400 --> 00:37:45,776
How can they be justified in taking tickets?

855
00:37:45,800 --> 00:37:47,936
The reason why the country is not prospering...

856
00:37:47,960 --> 00:37:50,800
is that the people's wisdom is not yet open.

857
00:37:51,000 --> 00:37:52,256
Meaning?!

858
00:37:52,280 --> 00:37:53,936
Playing mahjong...

859
00:37:53,960 --> 00:37:55,776
What does it matter whether the people are open or not?

860
00:37:55,800 --> 00:37:56,816
What did you throw my tiles for?

861
00:37:56,840 --> 00:37:58,256
You guys still want to lose face?

862
00:37:58,280 --> 00:38:00,016
Us Chinese people arguing amongst ourselves here...

863
00:38:00,040 --> 00:38:01,456
We let the foreigners see a joke

864
00:38:01,480 --> 00:38:04,256
Everyone else, go back to your cabin. Right now

865
00:38:04,280 --> 00:38:05,760
Let's go

866
00:38:07,000 --> 00:38:08,656
Mr. Zhongfu, are you alright?

867
00:38:08,680 --> 00:38:09,696
I'm alright

868
00:38:09,720 --> 00:38:10,736
General Yongcheng

869
00:38:10,760 --> 00:38:12,896
My discourteousness from before

870
00:38:12,920 --> 00:38:15,120
I formally apologize to you

871
00:38:15,720 --> 00:38:16,933
You are a fellow

872
00:38:16,957 --> 00:38:18,646
I'm ashamed

873
00:38:18,760 --> 00:38:20,800
Thank you sirs

874
00:38:21,640 --> 00:38:22,656
Sir,

875
00:38:22,680 --> 00:38:23,456
The boat ticket money...

876
00:38:23,480 --> 00:38:25,136
We will for sure return it to you as soon as possible

877
00:38:25,160 --> 00:38:26,416
No need no need

878
00:38:26,440 --> 00:38:27,616
We are all Chinese people

879
00:38:27,640 --> 00:38:29,216
Helping each other is what we should do

880
00:38:29,240 --> 00:38:30,640
Thank you

881
00:38:30,760 --> 00:38:31,696
Mr. Zhongfu.

882
00:38:31,720 --> 00:38:34,256
Your help, despite what happened yesterday,

883
00:38:34,280 --> 00:38:35,456
I wholeheartedly thank you

884
00:38:35,480 --> 00:38:37,760
What about the events of yesterday?

885
00:38:38,840 --> 00:38:39,776
You forgot

886
00:38:39,800 --> 00:38:41,376
At Waseda,

887
00:38:41,400 --> 00:38:43,760
I spit a mouthful on you

888
00:38:44,440 --> 00:38:46,176
How about if I didn't forget

889
00:38:46,200 --> 00:38:47,536
spitting back at you

890
00:38:47,560 --> 00:38:48,976
You spit a mouthful of phlegm on me

891
00:38:49,000 --> 00:38:50,416
it's your bravery

892
00:38:50,440 --> 00:38:51,376
Today's fight...

893
00:38:51,400 --> 00:38:52,736
is our bravery

894
00:38:52,760 --> 00:38:54,416
But it's only by bravery

895
00:38:54,440 --> 00:38:56,336
This fight is going to last until when?

896
00:38:56,360 --> 00:38:59,856
The principles in this, do you understand?

897
00:38:59,880 --> 00:39:01,536
I will wholeheartedly listen to your instructions

898
00:39:01,560 --> 00:39:02,816
Good

899
00:39:02,840 --> 00:39:06,096
Then let's go inside the cabins to chat

900
00:39:06,120 --> 00:39:07,456
General Yongcheng, please

901
00:39:07,480 --> 00:39:09,520
Let's go.   Come.

902
00:39:18,680 --> 00:39:20,240
Qiaonian

903
00:39:30,040 --> 00:39:32,640
Good  Now I won't be afraid of it falling

904
00:39:52,440 --> 00:39:53,840
Here

905
00:40:51,720 --> 00:40:54,320
Brother Yannian, Brother Qiaonian!

906
00:40:56,280 --> 00:40:57,456
What are you doing here?

907
00:40:57,480 --> 00:40:58,336
What good food are you eating?

908
00:40:58,360 --> 00:40:59,160
I also want to eat!

909
00:40:59,055 --> 00:41:01,810
{\an8}[Chen Zimei, daughter of Chen Duxiu]

910
00:41:06,200 --> 00:41:07,296
Aunt!

911
00:41:07,320 --> 00:41:08,568
Yannian, Qiaonian.

912
00:41:08,592 --> 00:41:10,416
{\an8}[Gao Junman, wife of Chen Duxiu]

913
00:41:10,440 --> 00:41:11,856
So hard to eat!

914
00:41:11,880 --> 00:41:13,680
What's wrong Zimei?

915
00:41:15,720 --> 00:41:16,816
Don't eat this anymore.

916
00:41:16,840 --> 00:41:19,120
Aunt brought over some buns for you guys.

917
00:41:21,000 --> 00:41:22,736
It just came out of the boiler.

918
00:41:22,760 --> 00:41:24,560
Eat the buns.

919
00:41:26,120 --> 00:41:28,080
Aunt, we won't eat it.

920
00:41:28,840 --> 00:41:30,016
Aunt is not an foreigner.

921
00:41:30,040 --> 00:41:32,160
What is it that you can't eat.

922
00:41:36,360 --> 00:41:37,856
You eat it

923
00:41:37,880 --> 00:41:39,760
Thank you aunt

924
00:41:42,760 --> 00:41:44,960
I brought you guys egg soup

925
00:41:55,160 --> 00:41:55,856
Here

926
00:41:55,880 --> 00:41:57,136
Fresh out of the pot

927
00:41:57,160 --> 00:41:58,800
Thank you aunt

928
00:42:03,000 --> 00:42:05,056
Yannian. Come, eat some buns

929
00:42:05,080 --> 00:42:07,776
Aunt, money is used to buy this

930
00:42:07,800 --> 00:42:10,800
When you look at it, it doesn't look good. Once you eat it, it's quite flavorful

931
00:42:12,040 --> 00:42:13,680
Where's Henian

932
00:42:13,880 --> 00:42:14,896
He's not feeling very well

933
00:42:14,920 --> 00:42:17,200
I had a neighbour help look after him

934
00:42:18,760 --> 00:42:20,096
Yannian, Qiaonian

935
00:42:20,120 --> 00:42:22,736
Aunt has come here many times to urge you guys...

936
00:42:22,760 --> 00:42:24,736
You guys are always stubbornly not willing to come home with me

937
00:42:24,760 --> 00:42:26,496
Your father is about to come back

938
00:42:26,520 --> 00:42:28,560
Come home with aunt

939
00:42:29,000 --> 00:42:30,496
We won't go back

940
00:42:30,520 --> 00:42:32,800
We don't have anything to do with this person

941
00:42:34,200 --> 00:42:36,560
But you guys working outside like this...

942
00:42:36,680 --> 00:42:38,176
is truly a lot of hardship

943
00:42:38,200 --> 00:42:39,936
Can't even get hot food to eat

944
00:42:39,960 --> 00:42:40,736
Come home with me

945
00:42:40,760 --> 00:42:42,496
Good or bad, you can eat something hot

946
00:42:42,520 --> 00:42:44,256
Okay?

947
00:42:44,280 --> 00:42:46,656
Aunt, don't try to persuade us anymore

948
00:42:46,680 --> 00:42:48,176
We will rely on ourselves

949
00:42:48,200 --> 00:42:50,320
This is our principle

950
00:42:50,600 --> 00:42:52,256
Zimei

951
00:42:52,280 --> 00:42:53,696
Your brothers are going to go to work

952
00:42:53,720 --> 00:42:54,976
This time we can't accompany you to play

953
00:42:55,000 --> 00:42:56,720
Next time, okay

954
00:42:58,760 --> 00:43:00,016
Let's go

955
00:43:00,040 --> 00:43:02,000
Goodbye aunt

956
00:43:04,520 --> 00:43:05,376
Wait a minute

957
00:43:05,400 --> 00:43:06,720
Here

958
00:43:06,920 --> 00:43:07,616
Take these all of these buns

959
00:43:07,640 --> 00:43:09,536
Older brother, you agreed that I would send you my grasshopper

960
00:43:09,560 --> 00:43:11,760
Brother promised you, I will do it for sure

